---

Case / Enclosure

For the enclosure, the circuit is designed to fit the following Takachi Electric Industrial aluminum cases:

Standard height version
Takachi Electric Industrial SPCP131808T
Marutsu Code: M0002-3623

This enclosure provides sufficient internal height to ensure safe mechanical clearance for the Nutube module, high-voltage power circuitry, and thermal stability while maintaining a compact footprint suitable for pedalboard use.

Low-profile version
For a thinner and lower-profile build, the following enclosure is also compatible:

Takachi Electric Industrial SPCP131806G
Marutsu Code: M0006-3822

Please use aitendo's "nutube10S" as the Nutube conversion board.
aitendo Code: P-NUTUBE10S

---

This version allows a slimmer pedal format while preserving the full electrical and sonic performance of the circuit.
